Question 3: Course Registration API
Model

Define a Course schema with fields: courseId, name, description, duration (positive integer), and students (array of student emails).

Endpoints

Add a Course (POST /courses)

Validate courseId (unique, alphanumeric), name, and duration.

Get All Courses (GET /courses):

Return all courses, optionally filter by duration.

Register a Student (POST /courses/:id/register):

Add a student’s email to the students array. Validate the email field.

Remove a Student (DELETE /courses/:id/unregister):

Remove a student’s email from the students array.

Delete a Course (DELETE /courses/:id):

Remove a course by its id.